name: tamara howell
text: One of my fav locations for delicious Pizza. great hospitality. the service was sociable and attentive. prices were fair for the quality of the food.

name: A B
text: Some people are not meant to operate a franchise! Location closed, was performing very poorly even before the virus.

name: sophia weaver
text: pizza... super delicious. fast, efficient, and courteous service.

name: Blueswan Games
text: This location, I have multiple and they have just hung up on me. I do not recommend ordering and if you do order, do it in person or online. NOT OVER THE PHONE!

name: Tah W.
text: I had pizza hut yesterday. Same ol same ol. But I still love pizza.

name: YILMAZ AKSU
text: I haven't ordered from hackettstown locations since they tell me it will be about 1 hour 30 to deliver in 2 miles distance, ones we complained about over baked pizza and uncooked wings.
